	* src/fade.c (xf86_gamma_fade): Add small delay
	after mapping window and before resetting gamma
	to avoid flicker.
	(ignore_all_errors_ehandler, safe_XF86VidModeQueryVersion) 
	(xf86_whack_gamma): Rename variable and use
	gdk_flush().

